Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇聖下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖下被…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉了
